in；元素总高度 = content高度 + padding + border + margin，即padding和border不包含在content尺寸内。</p><p>（2）怪异盒模型（IE盒模型）：元素总宽度 = content宽度（包含padding和border） + margin；元素总高度 = content高度（包含padding和border） + margin，即padding和border包含在content尺寸内。</p><p>3. 控制方式：通过CSS的box-sizing属性控制，box-sizing: content-box（标准盒模型，默认值），box-sizing: border-box（怪异盒模型）。</p>',NULL,40,40,40,'【错误点】无\n\n【改进建议】答案完美，继续保持！','',NULL,'AI',2,2,'2026-04-06 21:05:30',0,1,'2026-04-06 21:03:18','2026-04-06 20:32:09','2026-04-06 21:05:30',6),(85,45,14,9,43,'<ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeCreate：刚创建实例，data、method未加载</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>created：实例创建完成，按照template编译</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeMount：还没有挂载，DOM不可以访问</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>mounted：挂载完成，DOM可操作</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeUpdate：视图更新前</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>updated：视图更新完成</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeDestroy：实例销毁前</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>destroyed：实例销毁完成，</li></ol>',NULL,80,80,78,'【错误点】理解偏差、内容不完整\n\n【改进建议】请准确描述created阶段，此时template并未编译，而是data和methods已初始化。；在destroyed阶段，请补充说明清理定时器/事件等操作。；注意每个阶段的细节描述，避免遗漏关键点。','',NULL,'TEACHER',2,2,'2026-04-06 20:53:36',0,1,'2026-04-06 20:47:16','2026-04-06 20:32:51','2026-04-06 20:53:36',24),(86,48,14,4,36,'A',NULL,50,50,50,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34',2),(87,48,14,4,37,'true',NULL,30,30,30,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34',2),(88,48,14,4,38,'true',NULL,20,20,20,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34','2026-04-06 21:03:34',2),(89,49,15,9,43,'<ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeCreate：实例刚创建，data/methods未初始化。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>created：实例创建完成，data可访问，DOM未生成。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeMount：挂载开始前，template编译完成。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>mounted：DOM挂载完成，可操作DOM，发起请求。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeUpdate：数据更新，视图未更新。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>updated：视图已更新。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>beforeDestroy：实例销毁前。</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>destroyed：实例销毁完成，清理定时器/事件。</li></ol>',NULL,100,100,NULL,'【错误点】无\n\n【改进建议】答案完美，继续保持！',NULL,NULL,'AI',1,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:20:45','2026-04-06 21:17:15','2026-04-06 21:20:45',9),(90,50,15,4,36,'A',NULL,50,50,50,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59',2),(91,50,15,4,37,'true',NULL,30,30,30,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59',2),(92,50,15,4,38,'true',NULL,20,20,20,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59','2026-04-06 21:20:59',2),(93,51,15,1,44,'true',NULL,55,55,55,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18',2),(94,51,15,1,45,'A',NULL,29,29,29,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18',2),(95,51,15,1,46,'[\"A\"]',NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'AUTO',0,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18','2026-04-06 21:21:18',2),(96,51,15,1,47,'tru